Package: akNN
Type: Package
Title: An Adjusted K-Nearst-Neighbors Graph Construction Method for the Clustering of Single Cell RNA Sequencing Data
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: Jia Li (jia.li.1@vumc.org), Qi Liu (qi.liu@vumc.org)
Description: An adaptive approach to specify different k values for different points so that points in rare clusters have a lower k value and points in major clusters have a higher k value. 
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 3.6), Seurat, RANN, Matrix (>= 1.2)
Imports: Seurat, RANN, Matrix (>= 1.2)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
